<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.edwebproject.org/sideshow/" class="external text" title="http://www.edwebproject.org/sideshow/" rel="nofollow">From Sideshow to Genocide</a> - A history of the rise and fall of the Khmer Rouge, including survivor stories.</li>
