<li><a href="http://www.hawaii.edu/powerkills/SOD.CHAP4.HTM" class="external text" title="http://www.hawaii.edu/powerkills/SOD.CHAP4.HTM" rel="nofollow">Calculations for Cambodian genocide figures</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.btinternet.com/~andy.brouwer/vannnath.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.btinternet.com/~andy.brouwer/vannnath.htm" rel="nofollow">Cambodia Tales: Khmer Rouge torture and killing paintings</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.genocidewatch.org/news/CAMBODIA.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.genocidewatch.org/news/CAMBODIA.htm" rel="nofollow">Khmer Rouge Tribunal Updates</a> from <a href="/wiki/Genocide_Watch" title="Genocide Watch">Genocide Watch</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cambodiangenocide.org/hopes_fears_genocide_bp.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.cambodiangenocide.org/hopes_fears_genocide_bp.htm" rel="nofollow">Genocide of Cham Muslims</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.toreadnext.com/9780393322101" class="external text" title="http://www.toreadnext.com/9780393322101" rel="nofollow">When Broken Glass Floats: Growing Up Under the Khmer Rouge</a></li>
</ul>
